EXTRACTED VALUE: That's how it feels: brand extension, dilution rather than enrichment. [Mar 2008, p.102]
Madden 08 stands by itself as a respectable, rewarding sim, but judged in the context of last season, it's merely a mild, expensive improvement.
Stiff controls and samey puzzles hamper what is otherwise a fun, enjoyable romp.
Far Cry is like a car with a new coat of paint and a nice 19' set of rims. Nothing news, it just runs a little smoother.
